/*
Purpose:
- Analyse product-level revenue performance
- Identify which products contribute most to overall sales
- Support product prioritisation and strategic decision-making

Design Notes:
- Sales are aggregated at product level to assess overall contribution
- Results are ordered by revenue to highlight top-performing products
- This output is designed for high-level reporting and dashboard visualisation

Output:
- One row per product
- Total revenue per product
*/

SELECT
    product,
    SUM(sales_amount) AS total_revenue
FROM sales
GROUP BY product
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;

-- This dataset is used directly in:
-- Sales Performance dashboards to analyse product contribution
